CRM ( Transactional data )  ---> CPQ

ERP ( Ledgers )   ---> SAP, ERP, Peoplesoft

EPM ( Analytical data in multi dimensional databases )

Reporting 

----------------

admin builds model in plannning ( Capex, workforce, financials, project)
user enters budget input
system calculates totals using planning logic
data goes through approvals
financial budget is locked
actuals come from ERP
epbcs compares actuals with budget
forecast cycle updates using same drivers
rolling forecast uses planning logic
future budgets get refined using actual performance